# AeroSense MCP Environment Variables
# =============================================================================
#
# IMPORTANT: Claude Code does NOT automatically load .env.local files!
#
# After filling in this file, you must load the variables into your shell:
#
#   Option A (per session):
#     export $(grep -v '^#' .env.local | xargs)
#
#   Option B (automatic with direnv - RECOMMENDED):
#     echo 'dotenv .env.local' > .envrc
#     direnv allow
#
#   Option C (add to shell profile):
#     echo "source $(pwd)/.env.local" >> ~/.bashrc  # or ~/.zshrc
#
# =============================================================================
#
# SETUP STEPS:
# 1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env.local
# 2. Fill in your actual values below
# 3. Load into your shell (see options above)
# 4. Restart Claude Code
#
# The .env.local file should NOT be committed to version control

# ===================================================================
# GitHub MCP - Required for GitHub operations (issues, PRs, releases)
# ===================================================================
# Get your token from: https://github.com/settings/tokens
# Required scopes: repo (full control of private repositories)
GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
GITHUB_WORK_PAT=ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# ===================================================================
# Figma MCP - Required for accessing Figma designs
# ===================================================================
# Get your token from: https://www.figma.com/develpers/docs/api/authentication/
# Go to Figma → Settings → Personal Access Tokens → Create new token
FIGMA_TOKEN=figd_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# ===================================================================
# Trello MCP - Required for Trello board operations
# ===================================================================
# Get your API key from: https://trello.com/app-key
# Get your token from: Click "Token" link on the same page
TRELLO_API_KEY=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
TRELLO_TOKEN=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
